title: Central Government Inspection of Sections C1-C4 of the Kaohsiung Light Rail Completed Trial Operations Recently ...
text: ( Source : Kaohsiung City Government ) On the 25th , the Ministry of Transportation and Communications (MOTC) conducted its inspection of the first section of the Kaohsiung Light Rail Circular Line from C1, Lizihnei Station , to C4, Kaisyuan
